dct_title_s: ʾÂna [map] / bearbeitet in der Kartogr. Abteilung der Kgl. Preuss. Landes-Aufnahme.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading, form lines, hachures and spot heights. In upper margin: Karte von Mesopotamien. "3c." Includes guide to adjoining maps. "Nur für den Dienstgebrauch! Nachdruck sowie Benutzung zur Bearbeitung anderer Karten verboten." Shows route of the American Archaeological Expedition to Syria, 1904-1905, ruins, and places visited or seen by members of the expedition. Relief shown by hachures. From: Syria : Publications of the Princeton University archaeological expeditions to Syria in 1904-5 and 1909 ... Leyden, E.J. Brill, 1914-1930. In lower margin: Div. II, Sect. B., Pt. 3.
dct_publisher_sm: [Berlin] : Kartogr. Abteilung der Kgl. Preuss. Landes-Aufnahme, Februar 1918.
dct_subject_sm: Princeton University Archaeological Expedition to Syria (1904-1905)—Maps
dcat_theme_sm: Princeton University Archaeological Expedition to Syria (1904-1905)—Maps
